reviews.name: Trademark Fine Art "Elongated Window" Canvas Wall Art by Joval
reviews.reviewText: We originally saw this picture through another site many months ago did not get it and then regretted it started looking for it and although it was available on many sights you had the best price and the added surprise for me was I did not know you had so many things like this picture available on line that I can't get in my store but can have it delivered to my store at no extra cost, very pleased with my purchase and it looks great in my room thank you
reviews.title: LOVE IT

reviews.name: Trademark Fine Art "Elongated Window" Canvas Wall Art by Joval
reviews.reviewText: My kitchen does not have a window and I was looking for a picture that would seem like I was l looking out the window onto the ocean. This painting does the job! Very peaceful and welcoming.
reviews.title: Like looking out a window

reviews.name: Trademark Fine Art "Elongated Window" Canvas Wall Art by Joval
reviews.reviewText: In the pictures online, the painting's colors look faded. When I received this in the mail, I was pleased to see that the saturation was much more vibrant than what we see online! I don't have a window on one wall of my living room, so that was the perfect spot for this painting!
reviews.title: Just Beautiful!
